    "Additionally, the choice of programming language and AI model significantly impacts energy efficiency, warranting nuanced consideration.",
    "Developers are encouraged to stay informed about emerging technologies and actively participate in industry forums to contribute to the development of new standards promoting sustainable software development.The GSF assumes a pivotal role in establishing and maintaining green IT practices.",
    "Through collaboration with industry experts, researchers, and practitioners, the GSF continuously evolves standards for sustainable software development.",
    "The GSF's certification, Green Software for Practitioners (LFC131),foot_0 offers a comprehensive curriculum, equipping participants with the knowledge to implement Sustainable IT practices.",
    "Figure 3 shows a certification diploma of the completion of the course.Certification standards, exemplified by LFC131, provide a transparent framework for companies to measure and report their GHG emissions, fostering worldwide comparability and cost-effectiveness."
